import React from "react" import './index.css' class GoalieStatsTable extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super() } render() { let stats = this.props.stats let goalie = this.props.goalie let skating = this.props.skating let penalities = this.props.penalities return (
Season GP GS W L T OT SA GA GAA SV% GWG SO MIN
2020-2021 {stats.gamesPlayed} {goalie.gamesStarted} {goalie.wins} {goalie.losses} - {goalie.overtimeWins} {scoring.powerplayGoals} {scoring.powerplayPoints} {scoring.shorthandedGoals} {scoring.shorthandedPoints} {scoring.gameWinningGoals} {scoring.overtimeGoals} {skating.shots} {skating.shotPercentage}%
